title: Russian aviation conducted airstrikes at Slatyne of Kharkiv region, Serebryansky forest, Siversk, Chasiv Yar, Minkivka, Maysk...
content: Russian aviation conducted airstrikes at Slatyne of Kharkiv region, Serebryansky forest, Siversk, Chasiv Yar, Minkivka, Mayske, Ivanopillya, Toretsk, Selydove, Kalynove, Dachne, Romanivka, Velyka Novosilka, Sukhi Yaly, Shevchenko of Donetsk region, Temyrivka, Stepnohirsk, Prymorske of Zaporizhzhia region, - General Staff of Armed Forces of Ukraine reports
